   "source": [
    "in ridge regression for preventing our model from overfitting we add lamda*( m1**2 + m2**2 ...mn**2 ) to our cost function\n",
    "\n",
    "new cost function is = sum(( yi - yi_pred )**2) + lamda*( m1**2 + m2**2 ...mn**2 )\n",
    "\n",
    "other things are same\n"
   ]
